{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_011ATFHZbFe3fN4Liy4WtPTH","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01MetpwA3gcZ2bUiDy2HR6nX","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","old_string":"- Story was pre-created. Verification tags already present and correct.","new_string":"- Story was pre-created. Verification tags already present and correct.\n\n### 15-5-lint-rule-bare-exception-swallowing — dev-story (2026-03-25T06:55Z)\n\n**Problems encountered:**\n- `src/lib/scanner.ts` listed in story but has no Semgrep integration — actual Semgrep logic lives in `src/modules/observability/analyzer.ts`.\n\n**Workarounds applied:**\n- Semgrep test fixtures use annotation format but can only validate with semgrep installed. Vitest tests validate file existence/content only.\n\n**Code quality concerns:**\n- `no-bare-except-ellipsis` rule uses Semgrep `...` metavariable — matches ALL except bodies, not just literal Ellipsis. Correct per AC1 but name misleading.\n- Hook grep pattern `except Exception.*pass` is approximate — matches comments/strings too.\n\n**Observations:**\n- All 3799 tests pass. Zero regressions."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1474,"cache_read_input_tokens":48249,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1474},"output_tokens":46,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3fcb2b1c-e710-401b-91ab-b64a3e9a3996","uuid":"4d919fe7-a8a2-4ebb-ade0-33daeeaf47e7"}
