{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Vp95L6gFv69My2Jttqes2V","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Story 15-5: Lint Rule for Bare Exception Swallowing\n     2→\n     3→## Status: verifying\n     4→\n     5→## Story\n     6→\n     7→As a developer,\n     8→I want code review to flag `except Exception: pass` (Python) and empty catch blocks,\n     9→So that error swallowing doesn't cause silent production incidents.\n    10→\n    11→## Acceptance Criteria\n    12→\n    13→- [ ] AC1: Given code-review subagent reviews Python code, when it finds `except Exception: pass`, then it flags it as HIGH severity <!-- verification: cli-verifiable -->\n    14→- [ ] AC2: Given `post-write-check.sh` hook runs after writing a Python file, when the file contains `except Exception: pass`, then it prints a warning <!-- verification: cli-verifiable -->\n    15→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3fcb2b1c-e710-401b-91ab-b64a3e9a3996","uuid":"1c3e5406-b32b-4fab-b592-c86fd7fe8584","timestamp":"2026-03-25T07:04:29.599Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/15-5-lint-rule-bare-exception-swallowing.md","content":"# Story 15-5: Lint Rule for Bare Exception Swallowing\n\n## Status: verifying\n\n## Story\n\nAs a developer,\nI want code review to flag `except Exception: pass` (Python) and empty catch blocks,\nSo that error swallowing doesn't cause silent production incidents.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] AC1: Given code-review subagent reviews Python code, when it finds `except Exception: pass`, then it flags it as HIGH severity <!-- verification: cli-verifiable -->\n- [ ] AC2: Given `post-write-check.sh` hook runs after writing a Python file, when the file contains `except Exception: pass`, then it prints a warning <!-- verification: cli-verifiable -->\n","numLines":15,"startLine":1,"totalLines":107}}}
