{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Y3535ieV1tqJ2tRMTmvcUh","type":"tool_result","content":"  1298→| 13 | 3 | 0 | 3 (Docker) |\n  1299→| 14 | 1 | 1 | 0 (3 skipped) |\n  1300→| 15 | 10 | 6 | 3 (verifying) |\n  1301→| 16 | 1 | 1 | 0 |\n  1302→| **17** | **2** | **2** | **0** |\n  1303→\n  1304→Session 17 had the best efficiency ratio of any session: 2/2 attempted stories completed. The key insight was reclassifying verification tier rather than retrying the same failing approach. Sprint is at 64/66 (97%) with only 14-4 (stuck) and 15-5 (backlog) remaining.\n  1305→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01LQYjdJa1yDGbihRY8z3xfF","session_id":"3fcb2b1c-e710-401b-91ab-b64a3e9a3996","uuid":"6b91d6ec-ec2c-4815-b07a-8e84046e261e","timestamp":"2026-03-25T07:14:11.871Z"}
